Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------PRE------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表…表面性？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所谓的表皮冻伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.88,0:01:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差一点就变成真正的冻伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装着这种机械铠长时间走在暴风雪中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.52,0:01:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接部分的肌肉会被冻伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,润滑油也得换 不然行动迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫巴卡尼亚的人的机械铠不一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 医生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个头缠住了取不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.13,0:02:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我的头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.05,0:02:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的机械铠必须兼顾柔韧轻量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要有抗寒性能才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过多次测试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了用硬铝、碳素纤维
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.29,0:02:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及镍和铜等组合起来的机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我以为就是普通的铁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪破坏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 医生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是打算全告诉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.39,0:02:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位可是鼎鼎大名的国家炼金术师哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有银怀表
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种人居然相当于少校？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算在北地久留
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去换成寒冷地带专用的机械铠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专属的技师呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拉修瓦雷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客户要来北国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也不事先说明也不帮你换？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦不…我来北方的事没跟她说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死就让人家出差过来给你换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡100先士一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太诈啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且比东方司令部的还难喝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你大意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你装着那普通机械铠来这里干嘛的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不通过司令部自己跑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来想求助于阿姆斯特朗少将
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还带了介绍信来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女将军根本就不听人说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说要拔掉我的天线…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我？红豆丁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红 红…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 有意见就说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛 毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丑…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你们跟我弟弟阿列克斯很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然满身肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神采焕发呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啧」？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来说说你们不通过司令部就来找我的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那铠甲为什么是空的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一五一十全说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事我不希望太多人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的人大多都有自己的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被人知道的事又不稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这事被人知道了是要上军事法庭的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事我也做过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说我想她是不会放过我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是温莉是人质啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总统和人造人的事就不说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘀咕什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 就只说是为了恢复本来的身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在找带着这黑白猫的女孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你愿意帮助我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你们是思想浅薄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁莽行动扩大骚乱的蠢货了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想把这种人留在我的城堡里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 中央那些人怎么会放着这种人不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…虽然想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我对炼丹术有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认识这个会炼丹术的小姑娘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这技术我国没有 我想要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技术怕少不怕多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是在这个与大国德拉克玛接壤之地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼丹术似乎也能成为不错的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼丹术是偏重医学的技术啊 怎么能…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些只会在国内乱吠的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了是有人镇守国境
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们才能过上安稳日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方的国境线是由我来决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但凡有助于此 任何技术我都要得到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找那炼丹术女孩的事就交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不准离开要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 迈尔斯少校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们去干活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干活就没饭吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说得对…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的经历还真苦难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来像是习惯了战场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道他们内心还很天真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 还有些秘密没告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 要做什么工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这里的人都有些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也犯过什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光把我们的秘密都寻根究底问出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不公平了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修瓦尔人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说伊修瓦尔出身的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在歼灭战前都被肃清了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身上的确流着伊修瓦尔的血
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 祖母 父亲以及妻子都是不同民族的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这皮肤和眼睛的颜色是遗传自祖父的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美斯特利斯人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在我祖先之地伊修瓦尔可是尽情肆虐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修瓦尔人也放火烧了我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还杀了我们儿时玩伴的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 头一次有人这样回应我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在考验我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那场内乱之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人经常对我施以怜悯的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 真是烦透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我被伊修瓦尔人追杀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差点被绑架 之后又和解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟伊修瓦尔人的缘分还真是不浅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 人与人应该超越民族进行平等的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈尔斯少校在歼灭战时也在军队里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当时是阿姆斯特朗少将的辅佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来此赴任以后不久歼灭战就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以祖父为首 伊修瓦尔的亲戚都死在了东部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:10:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟军队肃清规定打了个擦边球 逃过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不恨军队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是会刨根问底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我讨厌无知的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是让你不开心了我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家炼金术师居然称自己「无知」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然憎恨军队的所作所为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时对继续任用我为辅佐的少将产生了疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承伊修瓦尔血统的我待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许会在军中引起风波
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她为何还不放逐我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾直接问过少将
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里格斯是个容不得半点差池的要地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,底层的每一个士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都必须在身为长官的我的意志之下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚强灵活且不为任何事而动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:10:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为一支强悍的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换言之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没工夫搞什么差别歧视
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你体内流淌着多民族的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够以多样化的价值观
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从各个角度观察这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在亚美斯特利斯土生土长的我要领导大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就需要你这样的人来辅佐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要胡思乱想 尽管跟随我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是合情合理 而且毫不含糊的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问她若是我体内的伊修瓦尔血统
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法原谅国军而闹事又怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们猜少将怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会代表国军 随时与你决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇 好可怕的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身后站着那么多部队还好意思说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「信不信老娘砍了你」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…的眼神来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的规矩知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是弱肉强食？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 弱者就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强者才能存活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,24小时365天不变的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分简单
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和官阶 人种 民族 男女都无关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是弱肉强食
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你运气够强所以活下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清除冰柱的人偷懒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你们的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你们做完了我让部下带你们参观内部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 够不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔曼准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔利克兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 不是被调到北方司令部了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 从北方司令部又被调到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成少尉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 恭喜你升官…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你为什么在这里清除冰柱？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然在做这种超底层的工作就说明…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没希望出人头地啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是开发层
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是阿姆斯特朗少将的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集结了国内最尖端技术 正进行兵器开发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有战斗用的机械铠？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 接着是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是布里格斯最下层
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和啊 跟上面差好远
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:14:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞内的生活线都集中在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使要塞上部受到攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地下的心脏部分也不会受到任何影响
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别挡路 让开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在这里乱晃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鲍比 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根管子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从地下来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在挖石头…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成德拉克玛的家伙在要塞下面挖地道？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很近了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦得要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 死也很麻烦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔尔夫·J·金布利？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在来这里的货车上身负重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被收容到山脚下的医院了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里格斯支部说要我们全面协助他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莲之炼金术师不是在服刑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说总统下令释放了他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有入侵者 从地下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早料到我们会来寻找对抗人造人的方法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 不…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央市的父亲大人跟你说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是来寻找恢复原来身体的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…挖洞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定没听父亲大人或者总统说过我们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:17:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们果然是德拉克玛的密探吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么和入侵者聊得那么亲密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲密个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(424,435)}（碍事…）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没说谎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…好宽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用再挖了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪对他无效？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 他要升到开发层去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知开发层
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该打中了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪类对那家伙无效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:19:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非战斗人员立即撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警报也关掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让德拉克玛那边察觉这里的骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大 弄过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试过车了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用试啦 这可是开发班的得意之作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把炮弹引信拔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一弹 装填完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛也…麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别发呆 装下一弹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…挖洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么杀都杀不死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会死？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么知道那东西的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:20:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌拖泥带水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的问题你能答多少答多少
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么知道那东西的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是德拉克玛的密探吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那东西是密探吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他认识你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像 不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能回答
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他是听谁的命令行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能回答
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不能回答
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你谅解…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底想不想帮我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看到这里的人们被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我那东西的身体到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体构造和成分应该跟人类一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟人类一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴卡尼亚 把坦克用的燃料拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浇到他身上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.48,0:22:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.06,0:22:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了没用的 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.81,0:22:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算放火烧他 也没那么容易…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道杀不死他 刚才的攻击很清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么只要让他停止行动就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让他尝尝比火焰更痛苦的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.70,0:22:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们见识一下布里格斯流的做法吧
